properties.description:
Can only be used in the context of a process. <br/> The script must be in groovy syntax and is executed before  the completion of a hauman task. <br/>It can be errors set, as seen in the example,  to prevent the completion the task.<br/>The form values are in the <b>"request "</b> object avalaible.<br/><br/><b>A example:</b><pre style="color:#212121;background:#cfd8dc;">def mitarbeiter = executeNamedFilter("employee_check.filter", [surname:request.name]).first()
def days = toDays(request.ende-request.start)
if( days <= 0){
  request.errors=[[
    path:'ende',
    message:'Das "Ende"-Datum muss nach dem "Start"-Datum sein.'
  ]]
}else if( days > mitarbeiter.remaining){
  request.errors=[[
    path:'ende',
    message:'Sie haben nur noch '+mitarbeiter.remaining+ ' Tage Urlaub.'
  ]]
}</pre>

